Quiz on Strings
What is the value of the variable A after the following code is executed?

A
# Write your code below and press Shift+Enter to execute 
​
A = "1"
A
'1'
Double-click <b>here</b> for the solution.
​
<!-- Your answer is below:
"1"
-->
